<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('head'); -%>
<body class="d-flex flex-column min-vh-100">
<%- include('header', {connexion:connected}); -%>
<%- include('modal'); -%>
<div class="px-4 py-5 my-5 text-center">
    <form method="post">
    <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">Life is short.</h1>
    <div class="col-lg-6 mx-auto">
        <p class="lead mb-4">Don't you want to make the change and save lives? You have this power within you. With our help, you can donate blood more easily and without effort.
            If you are looking for receiving blood, we are the one that can make it happen. Don't hesitate any more and be a part of this journey. </p>
        <div class="d-grid gap-2 col-6 mx-auto">
            <button name="donator" class="btn btn-primary" type="submit" >Become a blood donor</button>
            <button name="beneficiary" class="btn btn-primary" type="submit" >Looking for a donor</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    </form>
</div>
<%- include('footer'); -%>
</body>
</html>